{{kml}}
The '''70th parallel south''' is a [[circle of latitude]] that is 70 [[degree (angle)|degrees]] [[south]] of the [[Earth|Earth's]] [[equator|equatorial plane]] in the [[Antarctic]]. The parallel passes through the [[Southern Ocean]] and [[Antarctica]].

==Around the world==
