[[File:FagrifossJune.JPG|thumb|Fagrifoss in June 2010]]'''Fagrifoss''' is waterfall situated in Southeast [[Iceland]] near the [[Lakagígar]] region. It is located along the 4x4 road F206 approximately {{convert|24|km|0|abbr=on}} from [[Kirkjubæjarklaustur]] and {{convert|40|km|0|abbr=on}} from [[Laki]]. Access to the waterfall requires the crossing of a river ford, for which a 4x4 vehicle is needed.<ref><Enjoy Iceland>[http://enjoyiceland.is/Places/all_regions/attractions/Natural_wonders/231/default.aspx]</ref>

