{{expand language|topic=|langcode=RO|otherarticle=Ionel Haiduc|date=February 2015}} '''Ionel Haiduc''' (born 9 May 1937 in [[Cluj-Napoca|Cluj]]) is a Romanian chemist who was elected to the [[Romanian Academy]] and [[Academy of Sciences of Moldova]]. He was the President of the [[Romanian Academy]] between 2006 and 2014.
