{{Infobox airport | name = Machaneng Airport | nativename = | IATA = | ICAO = FBMG | type = Military | city-served = [[Machaneng]], [[Botswana]] | location = | owner = | elevation-f = 2900 | elevation-m = | coordinates = {{coord|23|11|05|S|27|30|00|E|region:BW_type:airport|name=Machaneng Airport (Machaneng)|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Botswana | pushpin_label= FBMG | pushpin_map_caption = Location of Machaneng Airport in Botswana | r1-number = 11/29 | r1-length-f = | r1-length-m = 1280 | r1-surface = Sand | metric-rwy = y | footnotes = Source: Landings<ref name="Landings">[http://aerobaticsweb.org/cgi-bin/search_apt?FBMG Airport record for Machaneng Airport] at Landings.com. Retrieved 2013-09-02</ref> Google Maps<ref name="Google">{{Google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?ht=en&z=13&t=k&q=-23.1845277777778,27.5009444444444+%28Machaneng+Airport%29|title=location of Machaneng Airport|accessdate=2013-09-02}}</ref> GCM<ref>{{GCM|FBMG|Machaneng Airport}}</ref> }}
'''Machaneng Airport''' {{Airport codes||FBMG}} is a military [[airstrip]] on the northeast side of [[Machaneng]], a town in the [[Central District (Botswana)|Central District]] of [[Botswana]]. The runway is {{convert|11|km}} west of the [[Limpopo River]], locally Botswana's border with [[South Africa]].
