{{Infobox Union |name= NCTL |country= [[Thailand]] |affiliation= [[International Trade Union Confederation|ITUC]] |members= |full_name= National Congress of Thai Labour |native_name= |image= |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Samut Prakan]], Thailand |people= [[Panus Thailuan]], president |website= |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''National Congress of Thai Labour''' (NCTL, {{lang-th|สภาองค์การลูกจ้างแรงงานแห่งประเทศไทย}}) is a [[trade union]] federation in [[Thailand]]. It is affiliated with the [[International Trade Union Confederation]].
